From 0000000000000000000000000000000000000005 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Boot Debug <noreply@qti.qualcomm.com>
Date: Mon, 30 Jun 2026 00:00:00 +0000
Subject: [DEV] qcom-distro.yml: build only qcom-multimedia-proprietary-image

Comments out the other three image targets (multimedia, container-
orchestration, networking) from the kas target list so dev rebuilds only
produce qcom-multimedia-proprietary-image. Drop this patch to restore the
full four-image build.

Upstream-Status: Inappropriate [local dev speedup]
---
diff --git a/ci/qcom-distro.yml b/ci/qcom-distro.yml
index da4f5dbe..848c6805 100644
--- a/ci/qcom-distro.yml
+++ b/ci/qcom-distro.yml
@@ -52,7 +52,7 @@ local_conf_header:
     SKIP_META_VIRT_SANITY_CHECK = "1"
 
 target:
-  - qcom-multimedia-image
+  # - qcom-multimedia-image            # disabled: build only proprietary image to speed up dev
   - qcom-multimedia-proprietary-image
-  - qcom-container-orchestration-image
-  - qcom-networking-image
+  # - qcom-container-orchestration-image  # disabled
+  # - qcom-networking-image            # disabled
